    <item>
      <title>土耳其里拉离岸利率因套利头寸解除而上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/turkish-lira-s-offshore-rates-jump-as-carry-positions-unwind</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在土耳其里拉持续下跌的情况下，交易员退出所谓的套利仓位，导致在长周末到来之前，离岸市场隔夜借入土耳其里拉的成本在周四大幅上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/turkish-lira-s-offshore-rates-jump-as-carry-positions-unwind</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 15:07:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
